   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-a" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>That's interesting. Could it be that you met another me from <FONT color=#a82424>Lagendia</FONT> who travelled through the <FONT color=#a82424>cracks in the dimensions</FONT>?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-b" mid="36" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>What the <FONT color=#a82424>Church</FONT> tells us is that <FONT color=#a82424>Goddess Altea</FONT>'s world is a fake one created from her dream so there are fake duplicates of us <FONT color=#a82424>Mistlanders</FONT> there and we may lose our body to them if we happen to meet them.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-c" mid="37" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Tell her about May.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>I'm curious what the person who looks like me is like.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-d" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>She's the kind who is interested in gossips and latest fashion and waits for prince charming...?<BR>……She may look like me but that sounds like a completely different person.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-e" mid="39" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Unlike her, I'm very realistic. <BR>Actually I wanted to be a scholar but my family is poor so I became a merchant. I still carry out my own research by collecting interesting materials.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-f" mid="40" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>When my thesis is complete, I'm going to send it to a renowned scholar and become his disciple. Before that, I must earn enough money to fulfill my dream.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-g" mid="41" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Is there anything I can help you with?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>I was thinking maybe I can hear some interesting stories from you, but actually I don't have much time for such chit-chat either.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-1-h" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Oh, you're talking about the fights at the Wasteland Battlefield.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Oh, you're such a nice person. <BR>Well, recently there has been a fight among the <FONT color=#a82424>Childs</FONT> and I heard they are using up a lot of weapons...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-1-h" image="QW_105.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-2" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>That's right. Can you go to <FONT color=#a82424>Wasteland Battlefield</FONT> for me and gather <FONT color=#a82424>scrap metal</FONT> that's scattered around there? I'll pay you well. It would be a good idea to use those scrap metal to make new weapons.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>If you don't see any scrap metal lying around... Well, you know what to do, don't you? <BR>Take the weapons from the people there and turn them into scrap metal. Huhu.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1871_trader_april-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-3-a" mid="46" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Ah I feel like eating steak... Oh?<BR>You must have collected the scrap metals already.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
