      <talk_answer link_index="n1871_trader_april-3-!next" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Merchant April$<BR>Thank you. If you're looking for more things to do, why don't you go to <FONT color=#a82424>Honest Merchant Pero</FONT>?<BR>He's a good man so it won't hurt.</html>]]></talk_question>
